{"tid":402384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做左本地遊戲公司3年，你問我答","createTime":"2017-09-16T11:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T21:55:59.000Z","uid":146714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"6e771eb5f2ad14d55590e014d5c00d776ff0d567","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:33:50.000Z","msg":"雖然當中有1年係編輯部<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有咩想知都可以問"},{"pid":"a1e871dcaf6e88840ff438a7eb50143c28199a20","tid":402384,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"本地有咩遊戲公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n唔係代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"1bc20c4874f81db91d99918955a0593f77671d92","tid":402384,"uid":57665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"Gameone"},{"pid":"49d6f397fd64545f86fcd4963eb991472e46934e","tid":402384,"uid":38957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:40:21.000Z","msg":"編輯部有咩做？人工點"},{"pid":"567da527084a6347858bee0895dc9d2a98544d32","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本地有咩遊戲公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n唔係代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n其實都係代理，黎黎去去果幾間，有巴打已經即刻估中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131b5a65f0436e0d25feaacb0be92b9369c78546","tid":402384,"uid":45551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:41:19.000Z","msg":"仲以為你寫game"},{"pid":"cff3c49d027fe07a458cf4ed69bc7ced8476b9d9","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>編輯部有咩做？人工點</blockquote><br />\n9k一個月，好鬼奀，但做既野身邊既人以為淨係打機出文咁，其實我星期六日都要出，有時仲要比隔離部門水鳩我出去做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然，有時仲要分身幫公司啲「自家遊戲」出啲繕稿打下飛機自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07aca7d4314418cfdd7b258595a13940c3d1c92a","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為你寫game</blockquote><br />\n我明白咁講好令人誤會係神抄果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我做果間都係有「自家遊戲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a569b5509b02f555e26a82ab452317fe5eef94a","tid":402384,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>編輯部有咩做？人工點</blockquote><br />\n9k一個月，好鬼奀，但做既野身邊既人以為淨係打機出文咁，其實我星期六日都要出，有時仲要比隔離部門水鳩我出去做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然，有時仲要分身幫公司啲「自家遊戲」出啲繕稿打下飛機自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個間嘢代理d手機game係咪全部都賺唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周圍都見到廣告，但好似冇見過身邊有朋友玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe95e5f980f6f63edb5b853bea3a224b6bfcb85c","tid":402384,"uid":92921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:46:35.000Z","msg":"有無靚女"},{"pid":"7a091498ae84531633136bd98ee8d0fff98d5262","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>編輯部有咩做？人工點</blockquote><br />\n9k一個月，好鬼奀，但做既野身邊既人以為淨係打機出文咁，其實我星期六日都要出，有時仲要比隔離部門水鳩我出去做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然，有時仲要分身幫公司啲「自家遊戲」出啲繕稿打下飛機自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個間嘢代理d手機game係咪全部都賺唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n周圍都見到廣告，但好似冇見過身邊有朋友玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得啲老fans會支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢拎果啲主題都係啲好耐歷史既作品，至於賺唔賺到錢我就唔肯定，我只係知我走左之後佢地由大office搬到細office<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5351fcd1d6c476d0731b8df23e603ec715a3a75","tid":402384,"uid":129729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"美術待遇如何 人工幾多？<br />\n入行難唔難？"},{"pid":"cbd859fdf25e78fd2833c81dcccd166d74840749","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無靚女</blockquote><br />\n你指公司入面啲同事定大時大節見到果啲？<br />\n公司入面肯定無，係靚比人推埋去做showgirl慳返筆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而大時大節果啲showgirl都幾固定下，不過負責聯絡果個唔係我，講唔得幾多，但值得一提既係我以前開頭撈編輯部果陣係要搵啲靚女出鏡交數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2b8c7936871940dc0432d02907670ae6bddcac","tid":402384,"uid":76601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"古龍真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faded067b6efeaae786901a3dff3e014d16af79","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美術待遇如何 人工幾多？<br />\n入行難唔難？</blockquote><br />\n答左入行果到先，入行我覺得唔算難，基本上佢只要有部門長期缺人都有機會入到，例如我當初係睇中佢編輯部要人直接入左去慢慢做，至於美術待遇方面就唔清楚，但應該無其他位咁陰功，印象中做啲野仲hea過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffd102327b0916ce3a7be06d4a4373d378aa9ce","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古龍真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN年前果隻緊係好，手遊我覺得好HEA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330cbd8a7ca0c2abf395948551cfa00c99219de7","tid":402384,"uid":4564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古龍真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實6.0之前一直都好多人玩，7.0變左免費之後外掛又唔捉，升到10.0果時直頭lag到on99趕走哂最後d客"},{"pid":"5e0b1924a5bb38dabd364ec3f4371e603ee4613f","tid":402384,"uid":4564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古龍真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN年前果隻緊係好，手遊我覺得好HEA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手遊隻隻都係同一個玩法，只你d角色樣、物品名唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前古龍d大幫靠整幫eq可以賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91169c83aed4886e9b8981bb235c8448adc49a8","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古龍真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN年前果隻緊係好，手遊我覺得好HEA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手遊隻隻都係同一個玩法，只你d角色樣、物品名唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前古龍d大幫靠整幫eq可以賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知道係有同事會整啲虛寶出黎賺鬼鼠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed3419666bc8a034de31f6ffdd4a5daa7aff166b","tid":402384,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"點解d代理game普遍都好lag<br />\n成lag日到玩唔到咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係公司租廢server 慳錢定網路公司廢?<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解會有代理呢個行業出現架<br />\n搞到d game低質晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8feaacc78de509d9e539cfadfb32219c0d34a6","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解d代理game普遍都好lag<br />\n成lag日到玩唔到咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係公司租廢server 慳錢定網路公司廢?<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解會有代理呢個行業出現架<br />\n搞到d game低質晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公司租廢server係lag機呢個問題上佔好大比重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其次都係取決返部機性能同網絡公司<br />\n因為我自己成日入測試服果陣好順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec1add5a0bbe389d0210a1797a0fa3b0e8ffd73","tid":402384,"uid":80503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"邊到宣傳多？"},{"pid":"191b46fbc990404b3748e2eacd884a422023cb81","tid":402384,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"到低好同廢server個價差幾遠<br />\n趕客都要租廢ser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca24b9ba47e50ea3def542a9b4587a8b97bd08ed","tid":402384,"uid":23525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>古龍真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN年前果隻緊係好，手遊我覺得好HEA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手你老母遊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131ce03da781009bbebeae9cf1f885e307d1c9ee","tid":402384,"uid":54124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"宜家去左邊到做"},{"pid":"d4f2dc4762b6cdf2f439d4781f47609ad736c7b6","tid":402384,"uid":106154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:17:55.000Z","msg":"哦！原來係你！我見你係邊個啦！"},{"pid":"6f114b17e6afb2ec54c322f28e789d53175f5898","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到宣傳多？</blockquote><br />\n通常都係編輯部自己做埋打手係網站同專頁出post，有時要入埋人地啲FB群組咁宣傳，有啲更明顯既係討論區，隔離台好似有個狗也不屌既活生生例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前game書仲係到既時候都會考慮入去落一兩頁廣告咁大把(當中果啲濕鳩攻略繕稿都當到一頁)"},{"pid":"e6dc1120a06598e89c45aacd16cbd024550b135f","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:20:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到低好同廢server個價差幾遠<br />\n趕客都要租廢ser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個價差幾多唔太清楚，因為係部門主管拉埋IT同老闆傾，咁老闆緊係慳錢至上會優先揀平啲既廢ser"},{"pid":"1a29d4a06e18af841a71ff35d1c69958ddaf9cf7","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>古龍真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nN年前果隻緊係好，手遊我覺得好HEA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n手你老母遊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住囉大佬，我當初負責左果隻垃圾手遊足足幾個月都有，好重怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64eaf75a97a1f405385f9275714b28fa8a018bf","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜家去左邊到做</blockquote><br />\n去完個旅行再決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為做咁耐無乜點放到假，啲假都係庶務部阿姐叫我放左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d3d37f478c81e60f78a4652c99594fd035aab0","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哦！原來係你！我見你係邊個啦！</blockquote><br />\n你可以試下估既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係普通員工一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時係online game一on就比人追住打既GM未試過做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41720b7873de20c640409bd011e740d70dcca504","tid":402384,"uid":57363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:29:39.000Z","msg":"Sd高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b3e870990f28a2a0b3067692d89c4447afbdb5","tid":402384,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到低好同廢server個價差幾遠<br />\n趕客都要租廢ser<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個價差幾多唔太清楚，因為係部門主管拉埋IT同老闆傾，咁老闆緊係慳錢至上會優先揀平啲既廢ser</blockquote><br />\n咪就係server lag, 趕走哂古龍d玩家...合緊狗無啦啦lag半分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就唔捉外掛，唔理隻game, 搞到隻game衰落，依家吸到少部分人回流，就出好多呃錢包，但個ser照舊lag"},{"pid":"319c599c74fa334ad9b551c6819becee3753fcbf","tid":402384,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"GO出名營運廢"},{"pid":"a6da67cdcb99cf2b623211cd7fb8fd6c8f68bf21","tid":402384,"uid":127937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:36:47.000Z","msg":"有咩前境咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無話有機會跳去邊d公司做咩game？同埋工作作息係點？會唔會帶D duty翻屋企做？"},{"pid":"010493ed4d559d1bdf7762d38b0aa2ea4440b7fe","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sd高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇住佢執，不過果陣我仲係編輯部，淨係見到有個同事成日係到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ccb4a001cd5c9849f5b3a11e02c6f782e22920","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GO出名營運廢</blockquote><br />\n我當呃工作經驗姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為一開始知道自己讀書唔掂，廢事再拎筆錢出黎讀IVE"},{"pid":"3ebc6290c389988cfac462dc37d5273580638b52","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩前境咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無話有機會跳去邊d公司做咩game？同埋工作作息係點？會唔會帶D duty翻屋企做？</blockquote><br />\n其實呢行都係跳黎跳去，真係睇黎識人方面夠唔夠落力<br />\n工作作息我最想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開頭編輯部真係病左都要係屋企出文，星期六日都要出，無得偷懶，而假設你凌晨見到有隻新game上架都要起身趕篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而轉左部門之後就長期OT多"},{"pid":"8bf9ad83c11f93c1e5d8feeeac82c7fb003e76e5","tid":402384,"uid":36712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"對港版天龍有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5768bd7689e657cfeacf304c7887efe16ff3548e","tid":402384,"uid":26976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"Gameone重製叮噹大富翁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e2db5841f9f2b8f35c6d71853a14a2712e5ea8","tid":402384,"uid":13280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"GO出左個使徒行者<br />\n入到appstore望左兩秒down都廢事就走左"},{"pid":"60a0b1882ec0e66ad041e385cf0510498e5a9c7a","tid":402384,"uid":25040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"如果想入行 有冇學歷或者 專業技能要求(畫圖丫 或 寫PROGRAM咁?)<br />\n<br />\n升職前景又會係點?<br />\n<br />\nOT有冇補水?<br />\n<br />\n依家都仲係9K 1個月?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7671a1b6cf40e610eb2b3344b7865c281f896d4f","tid":402384,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"點睇垃圾戲谷？"},{"pid":"0de4d8f042fdc92d0bf1a4ab3701ba5d58d7034c","tid":402384,"uid":114970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"對msgo有咩睇法"},{"pid":"9e99ec7f0e9ff4490ec6d3c348084f9ed14b9eae","tid":402384,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"做過手機遊戲代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你做既野差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc86cf30c0acbd515634764a8195a2a48579358","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對港版天龍有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年未入職果陣連埋班FD玩過，叫做過得去<br />\n但入職之後聽講傳聞有GM拎粒重樓玉出黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e844d0468d29d8cd04dc0c6b050a711345eb274","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gameone重製叮噹大富翁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該懷舊既又唔走去懷舊，失敗"},{"pid":"ec5721159dffb453a766b4e343ab16a66c17336a","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GO出左個使徒行者<br />\n入到appstore望左兩秒down都廢事就走左</blockquote><br />\n睇個勢都知垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個打手仲要hea做，係我就先踩CCTVB黎入一入題，不過做個打手都好多限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實放少少踩一踩自己反而效果會好啲"},{"pid":"9e5e0be2f64d6664c74748e9a1eef274bdecfa8f","tid":402384,"uid":55382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"有冇自己無限點數玩某隻game"},{"pid":"f6a7da4c5647387903a0d5867fdb011c18201b22","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果想入行 有冇學歷或者 專業技能要求(畫圖丫 或 寫PROGRAM咁?)<br />\n<br />\n升職前景又會係點?<br />\n<br />\nOT有冇補水?<br />\n<br />\n依家都仲係9K 1個月?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想入行好簡單，我唔識攝影但佢知我有部普通單反機都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升職你就要睇下你上面果個幾時走，我當初編輯部真係唔洗諗升職，轉部門就有得你諗下既<br />\n至於OT方面係無補水既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人工當然唔再係9k咁慘淡"},{"pid":"8a7ac53cfe1187797aaf8334330b15a5c496f2fb","tid":402384,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果想入行 有冇學歷或者 專業技能要求(畫圖丫 或 寫PROGRAM咁?)<br />\n<br />\n升職前景又會係點?<br />\n<br />\nOT有冇補水?<br />\n<br />\n依家都仲係9K 1個月?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想入行好簡單，我唔識攝影但佢知我有部普通單反機都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升職你就要睇下你上面果個幾時走，我當初編輯部真係唔洗諗升職，轉部門就有得你諗下既<br />\n至於OT方面係無補水既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人工當然唔再係9k咁慘淡</blockquote><br />\n依家幾k?"},{"pid":"fd1a28fce9cf29b1b5a520a39fcdf7cf36dc5f88","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇垃圾戲谷？</blockquote><br />\n揸好啲隻跑online啦，講真當年賣咁多廣告食個勢，依家幾大都試下代理埋隻手遊去賺返筆啦，不過依家呢代小學雞無左當時果份共嗚個勢又差緊啲。"},{"pid":"1be70d9bd44c66e1cb98f921aac43b02db4f2685","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對msgo有咩睇法</blockquote><br />\n果陣我要試玩陸服寫稿<br />\n隻game我覺得唔算太差<br />\n但去到港服睇住佢地搞啲營運方針之後感覺食相好差，係我離職必屌事項之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6caffddb1a8af957756e998ebe32b09ad22665dd","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過手機遊戲代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你做既野差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同時做兩個部門既野真係好似食兩舊屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349e5ce66ed0b24c5397c9c256aa13bf2ce8967e","tid":402384,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本地有咩遊戲公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n唔係代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</blockquote><br />\n其實都係代理，黎黎去去果幾間，有巴打已經即刻估中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得一個巴打估啫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3a07912dcb92ea40c221afc524ce89c222c000","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇自己無限點數玩某隻game</blockquote><br />\n我認仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咁做過，不過隻game幾廢，手遊黎，但你呢啲真係要偷雞得黎要拎平衡點，係可以上到全ser排名頭10名左右自high一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但見到排名咁上下既玩家衝左上黎就要放一放佢，等佢有成功感追落去，大概我係暗地裡咁做過"},{"pid":"4e18469441e9bacf70ca4ecf70a68bd853282a8c","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T14:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果想入行 有冇學歷或者 專業技能要求(畫圖丫 或 寫PROGRAM咁?)<br />\n<br />\n升職前景又會係點?<br />\n<br />\nOT有冇補水?<br />\n<br />\n依家都仲係9K 1個月?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想入行好簡單，我唔識攝影但佢知我有部普通單反機都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升職你就要睇下你上面果個幾時走，我當初編輯部真係唔洗諗升職，轉部門就有得你諗下既<br />\n至於OT方面係無補水既<img src=\"/ass