img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁睇落幾開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打你諗住繼續做落去 定 轉行啦?"},{"pid":"0b5a889542e50f78d9f3c2d77f21395ced3b569d","tid":402384,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"之前想入你公司但係冇回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ece4ecd5f83796ea33be312887b0e36b5270fd7","tid":402384,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:26:19.000Z","msg":"原廠活動係吸客<br />\n點解代理商出親既活動都趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739df078a2066e3e544f6f8ad133f2ce412b0d6c","tid":402384,"uid":60720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊到宣傳多？</blockquote><br />\n通常都係編輯部自己做埋打手係網站同專頁出post，有時要入埋人地啲FB群組咁宣傳，有啲更明顯既係討論區，隔離台好似有個狗也不屌既活生生例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前game書仲係到既時候都會考慮入去落一兩頁廣告咁大把(當中果啲濕鳩攻略繕稿都當到一頁)</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/387183/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/387183/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n是咪呢個，可唔可以代我當面笑佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87a776b62ac9660bcf29057183c524b0c8ea021","tid":402384,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"點睇game artist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bf17cae6d1c3674c1b816a7d0e6ef06bb35517","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gameone</blockquote><br />\nfg之前想入但冇回音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n建議你入第二間，不過先入呢間再跳都唔係話差，畢竟呢間似「新手訓練場」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5395f53b35d327becce345bae8b793d17c8c5d2","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果想入行 有冇學歷或者 專業技能要求(畫圖丫 或 寫PROGRAM咁?)<br />\n<br />\n升職前景又會係點?<br />\n<br />\nOT有冇補水?<br />\n<br />\n依家都仲係9K 1個月?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想入行好簡單，我唔識攝影但佢知我有部普通單反機都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升職你就要睇下你上面果個幾時走，我當初編輯部真係唔洗諗升職，轉部門就有得你諗下既<br />\n至於OT方面係無補水既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人工當然唔再係9k咁慘淡</blockquote><br />\n依家幾k?</blockquote><br />\n走之前12k個月，不過做既野都係同狗差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁番幾收幾？<br />\n每日既工作 就係寫稿同打機 出攻略咁？</blockquote><br />\n朝10晚7，所以都唔算話同人迫車果啲<br />\n每日工作你都算估得岩，但有時要幫老闆做啲打雜野，最開心拎住部單反出去啲發佈會到影女同呃野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁睇落幾開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打你諗住繼續做落去 定 轉行啦?</blockquote><br />\n去完個旅行再諗，應該會轉行，不過都係做返文職，始終算係「歎慣左」"},{"pid":"43b2834775f8bd451a15e892177196d514845ac6","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前想入你公司但係冇回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係掛，我咁廢都入到去做，正路點都做到下客服掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7deefa4fa7d4532e652fbe750199f3160f28b0ed","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原廠活動係吸客<br />\n點解代理商出親既活動都趕客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為怕行多步都奶野"},{"