blockquote><br />\n唔係話UI果D喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識3D係咪好窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbbfee0b54fddd33019627c228db65d9b6d51a6","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:21:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前想入你公司但係冇回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係掛，我咁廢都入到去做，正路點都做到下客服掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵咁耐工都冇見 GAME 公司請人<br />\n依份工係邊個網睇到定係FD介紹?</blockquote><br />\n我果陣係靠FD介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畢竟呢行始終都係識人好過識字"},{"pid":"bf7ddcdacb9bde04e1d871d89014cb69ce2a95c7","tid":402384,"uid":30214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"同事係咪毒撚多?"},{"pid":"e5a98d13a0987be418268fe310445fee36af34ce","tid":402384,"uid":135855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"有冇試過同啲YouTuber  夾埋宣傳？"},{"pid":"f77e6491ef67e3388336b119567adc564e1bda09","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點睇game artist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只能說辛苦佢地，次次見佢地都OT到好夜咁，不過好少有交集，最多係有bug話聲佢地知，遊戲系統上我都唔太敢再比意見佢地</blockquote><br />\n唔係話UI果D喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識3D係咪好窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見佢地有好多範疇咁，係搵工果陣蝕底啲咁姐"},{"pid":"cbc5fc8e65edbd1ef3a72cd05ab175dabe3bc753","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同事係咪毒撚多?</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最少我係其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54259d088702f971791d3d132d3725588a0d30d0","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過同啲YouTuber  夾埋宣傳？</blockquote><br />\n有，聯絡過光頭佬<br />\n我心諗明知倒米都搵，不過我都係收order做野，唔出聲，佢想打小學雞市場咪由佢"},{"pid":"2984aa004c886c28d7753c2ad35c48c72f57c7dd","tid":402384,"uid":127687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"我以前都做過呢間公司，感覺係比人呃左入去做，但team head又請我先離奇。<br />\n見工時team head話好簡單淨係做某樣野，但正式返工知道自己個title個心離一離，title完全係另一範疇嘅野，team head話要做嘅果樣野其實只係呢個title其中一個要識嘅基本，但我又叫做搞得掂，我諗無人知我係邊學邊做，同左個programmer講我情況佢都打左個突話我好野咁都搞得掂。<br />\n當時人工10k, 而家18.5k"},{"pid":"a8e8843af2cbd19bba47044db1becb15c098d332","tid":402384,"uid":146714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前都做過呢間公司，感覺係比人呃左入去做，但team head又請我先離奇。<br />\n見工時team head話好簡單淨係做某樣野，但正式返工知道自己個title個心離一離，title完全係另一範疇嘅野，team head話要做嘅果樣野其實只係呢個title其中一個要識嘅基本，但我又叫做搞得掂，我諗無人知我係邊學邊做，同左個programmer講我情況佢都打左個突話我好野咁都搞得掂。<br />\n當時人工10k, 而家18.5k</blockquote><br />\n係好搞笑，唯一抵賺既地方呢間公司當呃下經驗係唔錯既選擇"},{"pid":"ba6dd8ea95a7f6686e9c74ea2cb3e3e3698f42cb","tid":402384,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同事係咪毒撚多?</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最少我係其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會好難相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想投身遊戲製作行業 但又好憎同呢方面既毒撚溝通 做少少野都會好寡斷<br />\n搞到進程好慢"},{"pid":"e065ce360450284